Name: C-RUSH
About the game: C-RUSH is an old school Shooter, with HD graphics. A new threat is coming from the space; the plasma insects. Exterminate the vermin!! Beat your own score and compare it with the other players ! Key Features: - One ship with different positions to use - Different Gameplay according to the positions and shoots - A Schmup where you need reflection as well - Works with the XBOX 360 Pad - 2 Difficulty modes - Compatible with Steam leaderboards - Achievements to unlock! HD video here : C-Rush was made by 2 people only, and contains one world divided in 4 stages. This is a score game, the main goal is to improve your score each time you play.
